snippet.title: SHELTER Official Special Look & Trailer (2026) Jason Statham
snippet.description:
Official Shelter Movie Featurette & Trailer 2026 | More ➤ https://KinoCheck.com/App | Jason Statham Movie Trailer | Cinema: 30 Jan 2026 | Details ➤ https://KinoCheck.com/movie/jfl/shelter-2026?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=description
Mason is a reclusive man living in a remote setting by the sea. When he chooses to rescue a young girl from drowning in a terrible storm, he unwittingly sets off a chain reaction that soon brings violence his way, forcing him to confront choices from his past.

Shelter (2026) is the new action movie by Ric Roman Waugh, starring Jason Statham, Bodhi Rae Breathnach and Naomi Ackie.
